&lt;li&gt;Ensure applications meet &lt;strong&gt;security, compliance, and data governance standards&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay informed on &lt;strong&gt;emerging technologies and industry trends&lt;/strong&gt;, ensuring the team is equipped to support evolving business needs.&lt;/li&gt;
