&lt;li&gt;Conduct layer-1 trade investigations and validations with accuracy, and in accordance with approved processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Escalate complex matters to senior managers or relevant stakeholders with complete and timely information.&lt;/li&gt;
